graph TB
    User([User Message]) --> Classify[Classify Intent<br/>billing / technical / general]
    
    Classify -->|Billing| BillingAgent
    Classify -->|Technical| TechAgent
    Classify -->|General| GeneralAgent
    
    subgraph BillingAgent[Billing Handler]
        B_Search[Search Pricing DB] --> B_Generate[Generate Response]
    end
    
    subgraph TechAgent[Technical Handler]
        T_Search[Search Docs + FAQs] --> T_Generate[Generate Response]
    end
    
    subgraph GeneralAgent[General Handler]
        G_Generate[Generate Response]
    end
    
    B_Generate --> RiskCheck
    T_Generate --> RiskCheck
    G_Generate --> RiskCheck
    
    RiskCheck{Risk Assessment}
    
    RiskCheck -->|LOW: search, info| AutoApprove[Auto-Execute<br/>No human needed]
    RiskCheck -->|MEDIUM: refund, email| HumanGate[Human Approval Gate<br/>Slack notification]
    RiskCheck -->|HIGH: delete, admin| Block[Permanently Blocked<br/>Cannot proceed]
    
    HumanGate -->|Approved| Execute
    HumanGate -->|Denied| Deny[Inform User:<br/>Action not approved]
    HumanGate -->|Timeout 24h| Escalate[Escalate to Manager]
    
    AutoApprove --> Execute[Execute Action]
    Execute --> QualityCheck[Quality Check<br/>LLM scores response 1-10]
    
    QualityCheck -->|Score >= 7| Respond([Send to User])
    QualityCheck -->|Score < 7| Regenerate[Regenerate Response<br/>Max 2 retries]
    Regenerate --> QualityCheck
    
    Block --> AuditLog
    Deny --> AuditLog
    Respond --> AuditLog[Audit Log<br/>Every action + decision + reasoning]
    
    subgraph Checkpointing
        State[(LangGraph State<br/>SQLite dev / Postgres prod)]
    end
    
    HumanGate -.-> State
    Execute -.-> State

    style Classify fill:#8957e5,color:#fff
    style RiskCheck fill:#d29922,color:#fff
    style AutoApprove fill:#3fb950,color:#fff
    style HumanGate fill:#d29922,color:#fff
    style Block fill:#da3633,color:#fff
    style QualityCheck fill:#1f6feb,color:#fff
    style AuditLog fill:#3fb950,color:#fff
